                        <h1 class="u-mb-l u-fs-xxl">Answering separately from your household</h1>

                        <div class="page__body">

                            <p>If you need to answer separately from the people you live with, you can <a href="https://census-website-respond.netlify.app/end-to-end/ir-uac-request-launcher/?previous=website-answering-separately&current-journey=new-ir-uac">request an individual access code</a> to start a separate census, so they canâ€™t see your answers.</p>

                            {% call onsPanel({
