                            <h2>Access code by text message</h2>
                            <p>We will need your mobile number. This will not be stored and only used once to send the access code. The text will be sent from <strong>Census2021</strong>.</p>

                            <h2>Access code by post</h2>
                            <p>A letter with your individual access code will arrive in an unbranded envelope. The letter can be addressed to you, but we can only send access codes to the registered household address.</p>

                            <h2>If you want to fill out a paper census</h2>

                            <p>You can <a href="https://census-website-respond.netlify.app/end-to-end/uac-request-address/?previous=website-get-a-code&current-journey=new-hh-paper">request an individual paper questionnaire</a> to be sent in the post.</p>
